metadata.title: Water Basin Boundaries
metadata.description: This data is hydrographic in nature and is derived from U.S. Geological Survey (USGS) maps which are used for delineation of drainage basin boundaries. The boundaries are a further delineation of the USGS Hydrologic Unit Codes 19060501, 19060502, and 19060503 for the ANWR area.
metadata.notes:
Purpose: This dataset provide drainage area boundaries for areas on the coastal plain of the Arctic National  Wildlife Refuge.
